---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="CONTACT" description="OPOTOへのお問い合わせはこちらから。">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-32">
    <span class="font-heading-en text-sm tracking-widest text-muted">CONTACT</span>
    <h1 class="font-heading-ja text-xl md:text-3xl leading-tight tracking-tight mt-4 mb-8">
      お問い合わせ。
    </h1>
    <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
      撮影のご相談・ご予約、ギャラリーのご利用、その他お問い合わせは、以下のフォームからお送りください。
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- FORM -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 border-t-[0.5px] border-line">
    <form method="POST" action="https://formspree.io/f/mbdevnrg" class="max-w-xl space-y-8">
      <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://opoto.jp/thanks" />

      <div>
        <label for="name" class="block font-heading-en text-sm tracking-wide text-muted mb-2">NAME</label>
        <input
          type="text"
          id="name"
          name="name"
          required
          class="w-full border border-line bg-base px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:border-ink transition-colors"
        />
      </div>

      <div>
        <label for="email" class="block font-heading-en text-sm tracking-wide text-muted mb-2">EMAIL</label>
        <input
          type="email"
          id="email"
          name="email"
          required
          class="w-full border border-line bg-base px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:border-ink transition-colors"
        />
      </div>

      <div>
        <label for="category" class="block font-heading-en text-sm tracking-wide text-muted mb-2">CATEGORY</label>
        <select
          id="category"
          name="category"
          class="w-full border border-line bg-base px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:border-ink transition-colors"
        >
          <option>STUDIO(撮影について)</option>
          <option>GALLERY(ギャラリーについて)</option>
          <option>その他</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div>
        <label for="message" class="block font-heading-en text-sm tracking-wide text-muted mb-2">MESSAGE</label>
        <textarea
          id="message"
          name="message"
          rows="6"
          required
          class="w-full border border-line bg-base px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:border-ink transition-colors"
        ></textarea>
      </div>

      <button
        type="submit"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-heading-en tracking-wide border border-line px-8 py-3 hover:bg-surface transition-colors"
      >
        SEND &rarr;
      </button>
    </form>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script>
  window.addEventListener('pageshow', () => {
    (document.querySelector('form') as HTMLFormElement)?.reset();
  });
</script>
